indir = Path(tempfile.mkdtemp())
fasta_file_1_fasta = tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(mode='w+', dir=indir,
    encoding='utf-8', suffix='.fasta')
fasta_file_1_fasta.write('>Header\nATCG')
fasta_file_1_fasta.flush()
fasta_file_2_fna = tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(mode='w+', dir=indir,
    encoding='utf-8', suffix='.fna')
fasta_file_2_fna.write('>Header\nATCG')
fasta_file_2_fna.flush()
fasta_file_3_fa = tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(mode='w+', dir=indir,
    encoding='utf-8', suffix='.fa')
fasta_file_3_fa.write('>Header\nATCG')
fasta_file_3_fa.flush()
sample_name_dict = get_sample_name_dict(indir=indir)
assert len(sample_name_dict) == 3
shutil.rmtree(indir)
